Twitter: @Unexplained Who is that? What are they doing? Are they ok? Are they coming for me?
ID: 10627066 2. Welcome to Ireland’s Leap Castle, home to a mysterious spirit, called “ The Elemental .” View this image › 
Twitter: @TheExtraDude Apparently, “The Elemental” spirit protects the castle, which is “used for initiations and druidic magick.”
ID: 10627736 3. A ghost will probably come for YOU if you visit Jablanica Lake in Bosnia. The lake dried up and casually revealed a cemetery. View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10627304 4. In Hawaii there are anthropomorphic lava formations that look like they’re straight from the underworld. View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10627180 5. And In Poland there is “ Crooked Forest, ” where you know shit has gone down: View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10627140 6. Can you imagine flower-picking and seeing this extremely creepy case of “ dead man’s fingers ”? View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10627229 7. Or you’re taking a nice hike in the forest, and suddenly it’s like, “Oh, look a tree that looks like a woman/crucifixion!” View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10627203 8. Speaking of forests — where literally nothing good ever happens — can you fathom running into this acrobatic apparition ? Video of a strange figure recorded in the woods of Indonesia.
— The Unexplained (@Unexplained) ID: 10627751 9. Or reaching the middle of the woods to find a bunch of missing person fliers . A man hiking through the woods in Long Island came across what looked like a scene out of a horror film. Via NY Post
— The Unexplained (@Unexplained) NY Post ID: 10627791 10. And if I’m driving and EVER come across this shit , I’m turning the hell around. Imagine driving late at night and seeing this...
— The Unexplained (@Unexplained) ID: 10627101 11. Wait, can anyone explain this Hitchcock-style crow invasion ? View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10627747 12. Or even worse, this beetle invasion in Argentina? View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10628144 13. At least it wasn’t an invasion of caterpillars, like this one that looks like Edgar Allen Poe. View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10627757 14. And can I help you with something, possessed doll from Singapore ? View this image › 
reddit.com ID: 10628087 15. Was it you who wrote this message in an abandoned church? View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10627288 16. Or maybe you wrote this one , found in an abandoned home in Massachusetts? View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained “I love you. More than you know. I’ve missed you since you died. Please stop visiting.”
ID: 10628112 17. And what the devil is Satan doing above this innocent little church? View this image › 
Twitter: @Unexplained ID: 10627765 18. Seriously, what the HELL ? View this image ›
